description:
Spherical Harmonics V2 is an NFT collection of 10,000 1 of 1 procedurally generated shapes and patterns.  All equally rare, beautiful and special in its own particular way.

This collection was created by Luis Pages (@PAGESVFX) a veteran of the visual effects industry with film credits such as Avatar, Gravity, Harry Potter 5 and many more.  

My procedural system takes into consideration hundreds of thousands of shape variations, color ranges and noise patterns, as well as 87 different lighting and reflection scenarios to produce millions of unique possibilities. 

I hope you enjoy my collection.
name: Spherical Harmonics V2
